<![CDATA[<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 17.12px; background: white;">Hi {!Lead.FirstName},<br></span><br><font face="arial">I’ve been unable to reach you since you requested a call back.<br></font><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>This means I’ve been unable to provide you with the business insurance quote you requested.<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>If you are&nbsp;</span><b style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">interested in proceeding with your quote</b><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">, just let me know the best date and time for me to call you. Alternatively you can give me a ring on&nbsp;</span><b style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">01242 808 740</b><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif">.<br></font></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" style="background-color: white;"><br></font><font face="arial"><span style="background-color: white;">Kind regards,</span><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></span></font></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></span></font><font face="Arial, sans-serif">{!User.FirstName}<br></font></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Sales Team<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br><font face="Arial, sans-serif">E: salesteam@kingsbridge.co.uk<br></font></span><font style="font-size: 12pt;">T:&nbsp;</font><font style="font-size: 12pt;">01242 808740</font></p>]]></td>
</tr>
